First you have to create a directory called src, and then put your data in this directory. Each class should put in one directory, such 0, 1, 2, 3..., then run simplerename.
Then create three directories: train, verify and test. run the rebuild.py, and input the factor of train , verify and test like: 70, 15 and 15.
Run binAndCrop to bin and crop the images to fixed size.
Finally, run createDataSet.py to create the pkl.gz file, this file is the input of the convolutional neural networks.
